data.description: AMAZING PRICE DROP for this awesome 5 bedroom/3.5 bathroom home in the desired Fairway Estates subdivision!  Home is as spacious as can be and overlooks the gorgeous neighborhood pond w/fountain! Beautiful hardwood floors throughout the main level! Formal dining room for all your extra dining needs!!  Very open from kitchen to family room with a see thru fireplace! Tons of kitchen cabinets with granite counters!! 4 spacious bedrooms on upper level - good closet space - Master bedroom/suite is a great size with a jacuzzi tub and tiled shower! Lower level is cozy with great space - has the 5th bedroom and a full bathroom!! Good storage as well! Walks out to a patio and fenced yard! Three car garage for your car needs or extra storage! Lansing School District! Don't miss this great price reduction!!
